Starting this week (March 23) this class is moving online. We will use the following online resources:
. DataCamp. You need to sign up for it, using the [https://www.datacamp.com/groups/shared_links/5188e189b8369c5687fba1bb1c9792a5207eea8f3829bac8aeaebfbd9ee5345a invite link]. You will need to use your @masonlive.gmu.edu email to get free access. 
. Stanford's [https://online.stanford.edu/courses/sohs-ystatslearning-statistical-learning Statistical Learning] class.
. [http://faculty.marshall.usc.edu/gareth-james/ISL/ ISLR Book]
. [https://piazza.com/gmu/spring2020/568/home Piazza] for discussing HW\/project\/midterm. You can sign up [https://piazza.com/gmu/spring2020/568 here]

